{
  "id": "adv_event_2210_01_05_01",
  "title": "星の海の記憶",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_05-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "星見市のみなさん、新生LizNoirの\nライブ楽しんでますかーっ！　元気ですかーっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone from Hoshimi City‚ are you enjoying\nthe live performance of the new LizNoir? How are you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 9.9274145126,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7600.000000000001
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 10.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_05-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "みんな、もうこころの魅力に夢中ですね！\nでは、ダメ押しに莉央さんのモノマネを――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone has already fallen in love with Kokoro’s charm!\nWell‚ here’s my imitation of Rio-san’s voice――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.1333333333,
      "endTime": 17.7094559033,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 17.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_05-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "LizNoirに笑顔はいらな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "LizNoir doesn't need a smile…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.9,
      "endTime": 20.5653287411,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_laugh-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7700.000000000003
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 20.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_05-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっ、こころ、脱線しないの！\nもー、すみませーん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ Kokoro‚ don't go off track!\nOh my~ I'm sorry~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.6333333333,
      "endTime": 26.0984184544,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 27.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_05-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "みんな、リーダーの莉央からお願いがあるんだ\n聞いてほしい。……莉央",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone‚ leader Rio has a favor to ask‚\nso I hope you’ll listen to it… Rio",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.2,
      "endTime": 33.5888774991,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 6599.999999999998
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 33.8
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 36.2
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 38.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_05-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう、葵",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you‚ Aoi",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.8,
      "endTime": 40.626485204699996,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8533.3333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 42.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_05-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "……みなさん、今から一つ\n私のお願いを聞いてほしいんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Everyone‚ could you please‚\ndo me a favor from now on?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.2333333333,
      "endTime": 47.6213250608,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_05-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "今から特別に聴いてもらいたい歌があります\n……LizNoirではない、あるアイドルの曲です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There is a song I would like you to listen to specially from now on.\n… It's not LizNoir‚ it's a song by some idol.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.6,
      "endTime": 57.600000000099996,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 14899.999999999998
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_05-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "三年前の曲だけど……私の大好きな歌\n聴いてくれますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Although it’s a song from 3 years ago… my favorite song.\nCould you please listen?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.9333333333,
      "endTime": 64.1950770629,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 67.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_05-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう。では、彼女と一緒に歌いたいと思います\nどうぞ――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you. Then I'll sing with her.\nCome on in――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.3666666667,
      "endTime": 74.4333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 7599.9999999999945
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 16233.333333299996
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 74.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 77.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_05-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "みなさん、こんばんは\n月のテンペストの長瀬琴乃です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hello everyone\nThis is Kotono Nagase from Moon Tempest.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.5333333333,
      "endTime": 84.2030974806,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 85.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_05-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "みなさんもご存じの通りLizNoirは\n今私達と同じ星見プロダクションに所属しています",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As you all know‚ LizNoir is now under Hoshimi Productions‚\nthe same company as us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.4333333333,
      "endTime": 93.23333333330001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 93.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_05-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "LizNoirはかつて私達とNEXT VENUS\nグランプリで戦った、ライバルです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "LizNoir is our former rival\nat the NEXT VENUS Grand Prix.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.4333333333,
      "endTime": 99.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_05-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "でも、同時に大切な仲間です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But‚ they are also valuable colleagues.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.9333333333,
      "endTime": 103.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 103.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_05-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "私だけじゃありません、私の姉――\n長瀬麻奈にとってもLizNoirは特別な存在でした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "LizNoir was a special person not only to me‚\nbut also to my sister―― Mana Nagase.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.3,
      "endTime": 112.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 113.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_05-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "姉がアイドルを目指したきっかけは\nこのライブハウスでLizNoirの――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The reason my sister dreamed of becoming an idol\nwas because she heard LizNoir's songs――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.1333333333,
      "endTime": 118.87134796580001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 119.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_05-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さんと葵さんの歌を聴いたから――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio-san and Aoi-san at this live house――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.0666666667,
      "endTime": 122.074376456,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 120.3
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 122.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_05-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "今日、私は、そんなLizNoirと\nこのステージに立てて……とても嬉しいです……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Today‚ I get to stand on this stage with LizNoir…\nI'm so happy…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.5,
      "endTime": 128.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 128.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_05-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.7,
      "endTime": 130,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 130.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_05-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "……こちらこそ光栄だね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "… We are honored too",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131,
      "endTime": 134.0747392654,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 134.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
